ygData.messageBody:
Hey Wolfie,<br>I got this for Xmass, so that's
how new I am.<br>I am the one with the two on post.
Anyway, what I have done and still am, is to go to every
site about EverQuest and start looking thru all their
material. Alot of these people are WizBang at their
characters, so listen and learn from them, I am.<br>Get
Stradgy guide, read learn terms,chat,emoticons,get quests
for good bucks.<br>My HighElf Wizard has over 2Plat
in the bank already just doing quests for the
npc's.<br>Anyway hope this helps and if you decide to do either
one of my characters give me a /wave ;-)<br>Good Luck
& Good Hunting!<br>Cat
